snippet.title: Amber Heard Rumors Debunked| Sean O'Connells book drops| Wishing Zack Snyder Happy Birthday & More
snippet.description:
Tonight on T.Y's Corner the Daily SHow, Well Be jumping into the Golden Globes Biggest Winners, Overlooks, And Moments. Also, We'll be Discussing Recent rumors Surrounding Amber Heard's Character in Aquaman, "Mera". Fans Show Director Zack Snyder Love & Support For His Birthday, And Sean O'Connell's Book Hitting Shelves Today! #ZackSnydersJusticeLeague #DCEUNews #GoldenGlobes
